{"tid":432391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，份人都係冇乜感情？","createTime":"2017-10-11T13:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T11:23:56.000Z","uid":133638,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d29af15675a22727f5621a91922990956cbab4ee","tid":432391,"uid":133638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"本性就ok善良  係咁意都幫下手（捐下錢咁） <br />\n但係親情 友情 戀情都係冇乜感覺 <br />\n日常生活都只係喺人面前扮下笑 扮下有興趣 扮下野咁 <br />\n但實際心入面只係覺得無聊 冇乜野咁？<br />\n而家諗野都係好撚實際 對錯為先 反而側重情又真係冇乜<br />\nSorry For 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5d47a7e20e119ae63d6ca5a2e7c8bc4307debd","tid":432391,"uid":3701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"同你有少少似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未至於覺得無聊 但有時對呢啲野會無咩感覺"},{"pid":"1d9f251b4e1e543eb809cfa9d39d2ee3a0d6fb87","tid":432391,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56da711c9e4c3ff6ad7a10473eb6fedb6e16a15","tid":432391,"uid":76105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無無聊聊又一日 <br />\n覺得身邊既野好幼稚無謂，提唔起興趣"},{"pid":"ca4d620f20fee040e7fc9540b3fcbfc978c3a49c","tid":432391,"uid":117238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:36:40.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 諗野理性分析行先<br />\n曾經有親戚過左身其他人係醫院喊<br />\n自己就一滴眼淚都無流過因爲覺得人終須一死係好自然既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8549d36fd117384f1bf3b1278ac358a6b17f1489","tid":432391,"uid":542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"我曾經都咁諗過<br />\n可能只係你未遇到"},{"pid":"56a0474ff1ec03a57a552733