aces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b9a0493bee5338bddb2e7b73bef1896dbb1260","tid":432391,"uid":133638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你一樣 諗野理性分析行先<br />\n曾經有親戚過左身其他人係醫院喊<br />\n自己就一滴眼淚都無流過因爲覺得人終須一死係好自然既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame...我去到連老豆過身果時都無<br />\n<br />\n有時好有罪惡感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有時都會咁諗<br />\n但睇過有心理分析話呢種壓抑情感、潛意識既防禦機制之所以存在係因為過去曾經保護過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我又唔會覺得好自責or覺得自己好有問題要改</blockquote><br />\n總係覺得係因為之次啲事太刺激 而家有抗性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3216a2c2e921a04fadde479492b1630d671d7b7d","tid":432391,"uid":133638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你一樣 諗野理性分析行先<br />\n曾經有親戚過左身其他人係醫院喊<br />\n自己就一滴眼淚都無流過因爲覺得人終須一死係好自然既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame...我去到連老豆過身果時都無<br />\n<br />\n有時好有罪惡感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有時都會咁諗<br />\n但睇過有心理分析話呢種壓抑情感、潛意識既防禦機制之所以存在係因為過去曾經保護過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我又唔會覺得好自責or覺得自己好有問題要改</blockquote><br />\n總係覺得係因為之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>啲事太刺激 而家有抗性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aa1b9841617ffca9070851380bb8d9649ff40bbd","tid":432391,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"對咩都無咩feel<br />\n無鍾意過人<br />\n好感都係好快就無<br />\n個心好平靜好似唔見左"},{"p